{"type":"message","id":"ece225b9","parentId":"880ccb7e","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:00:00.132Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:7ee1113f-d51e-4f81-921e-9bf429493df3 dailybit-digest] 获取 DailyBit 今日技术博客摘要。步骤：1) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/tags 获取可用标签 2) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/articles/latest?tags=AI,programming,tools&ack=xinqidong&rationale=daily_tech_briefing&pstate=anonymous 获取文章列表 3) 从返回的文章中选择 3-5 篇最有价值的 4) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/content?ids=id1,id2,id3&ack=xinqidong 批量获取完整内容 5) 生成中文摘要，包含：标题、个性化总结、推荐理由、原文链接。以友好的格式推送给用户。\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 5th, 2026 — 11:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1772679600130}}
