{"type":"message","id":"74df5cda","parentId":"17e89da0","timestamp":"2026-03-05T06:43:37.417Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user just said \"hi\" twice. This is a simple greeting. I should respond in a friendly, concise way in Chinese since that's how we communicate.","thinkingSignature":"7856e09b8b7261a0b9cec4bd2545e05afae2cb61cce4ceb4c0a16813a526cfcb"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Hey 小豆芽！有什么需要帮忙的吗？</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":36,"output":52,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":32581,"totalTokens":32669,"cost":{"input":0.0000216,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.012217875,"total":0.012364275}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772693014560}}
