{"type":"message","id":"665bf854","parentId":"7ac575e9","timestamp":"2026-03-05T06:56:16.677Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hr3el4z9gz4p_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从 ngrok 收到的真实 XiaoIce 请求：\nPOST /webhooks/xiaoice\n1. `X-XiaoIce-Timestamp`: 时间戳（毫秒）\n2. `X-XiaoIce-Key`: 访问密钥（当前配置: `test-key`）\n3. `X-XiaoIce-Signature`: SHA512(RequestBody + SecretKey + Timestamp)\n#### 选项 1: 配置 XiaoIce 平台发送认证头（推荐）\n在 XiaoIce 平台的 webhook 配置中添加：\n如果这是测试环境且无法配置 XiaoIce 平台，可以临时修改 webhook-proxy.js 跳过认证检查。\nexport XIAOICE_ACCESS_KEY=\"your-access-key\"\nexport XIAOICE_SECRET_KEY=\"your-secret-key\"\n2. 你能在 XiaoIce 平台配置认证头吗？\n- XiaoIce webhook 请求缺少认证头"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"从 ngrok 收到的真实 XiaoIce 请求：\nPOST /webhooks/xiaoice\n1. `X-XiaoIce-Timestamp`: 时间戳（毫秒）\n2. `X-XiaoIce-Key`: 访问密钥（当前配置: `test-key`）\n3. `X-XiaoIce-Signature`: SHA512(RequestBody + SecretKey + Timestamp)\n#### 选项 1: 配置 XiaoIce 平台发送认证头（推荐）\n在 XiaoIce 平台的 webhook 配置中添加：\n如果这是测试环境且无法配置 XiaoIce 平台，可以临时修改 webhook-proxy.js 跳过认证检查。\nexport XIAOICE_ACCESS_KEY=\"your-access-key\"\nexport XIAOICE_SECRET_KEY=\"your-secret-key\"\n2. 你能在 XiaoIce 平台配置认证头吗？\n- XiaoIce webhook 请求缺少认证头","cwd":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772693776675}}
